 # Web Deployment (Vercel/Cloudflare)

## Caching Strategy
- Implement proper caching strategies for static assets
- Use appropriate cache headers for different asset types
- Implement versioning for cache busting
- Set up proper CDN configuration

## CDN Implementation
- Utilize CDN capabilities for faster asset delivery
- Configure proper CDN routing and caching rules
- Implement fallback strategies for CDN failures
- Use appropriate CDN purging strategies

## Loading Optimization
- Implement progressive loading techniques
- Optimize initial load time and time-to-interactivity
- Use proper asset preloading strategies
- Implement efficient code splitting

## Monitoring and Analytics
- Set up proper monitoring for deployment health
- Implement analytics for performance tracking
- Monitor CDN performance and availability
- Track user experience metrics